Title: Claire Chase Classic Sports Valise Cafe 316 CFE
Description: Pack, carry, and transport your short trip necessities neatly, comfortably, smartly, and stylishly in the Claire Chase Classic Sports Valise in Cafe. This soft, smooth, supple, and luxurious top-grain cowhide leather bag features a classic, compact and structured, multi-compartment design with shiny, custom hardware, and it's available in several colors. It boasts a spacious, lined main compartment with a convenient, u-shaped, zippered opening; zippered end compartments perfect for holding your shoes and accessories; a roomy, flat zippered pocket ideal for stashing your travel documents in; and a front gusseted, zippered compartment for organization and quick access to frequently-needed items. It comes with both wrapped, rolled double handles and a padded, adjustable shoulder strap, and it makes a terrific carry-on! Product Features: Meets airline requirements for carry-on luggage. Double zipper opening across top for easier access.Deluxe antique brass hardware.Four zipper compartments, one Velcro compartment all wet lined.Comfortable, adjustable all leather shoulder strap with pad.Velcro closure handle.Handsome leather ID tag Size: Small Dimensions: 18" x 11" x 10" Weight: 5 lbs Material: Cowhide Leather Warranty: 3 year limited warranty against factory defects Linear Inches: 39" SKU: 316E Free Monogramming up to 3 initials for a limited time!
